        <![CDATA[
        <h2>Termux+ v2.0.0</h2>
        <p>A modular, AI-enhanced terminal environment for Android, supporting plugins and advanced integrations.</p>
        
        <h3>Features</h3>
        <p>• Modular Plugin System</p>
        <p>• Native AI Integration (Claude, etc.)</p>
        <p>• Gboard autocomplete in terminal</p>
        <p>• Multi-tab & Multi-window support</p>
        <p>• Mobile-optimized gestures</p>
        
        <h3>Built on Termux</h3>
        <p>This app is a fork of the original Termux project with extensive enhancements.</p>
        
        <p><b>Original Termux:</b> https://github.com/termux/termux-app</p>
